short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Replace search engine with Autumn Tab Search!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Autumn Tab Search enhances your browser experience by replacing your default search engine with its custom solution. Search results are provided by our trusted partners, ensuring a secure and efficient browsing experience through HTTP redirects.

By selecting "Add to Chrome," you authorize the installation of the "Autumn Tab Search" extension, set Autumn Tab Search as your default search engine in Chrome, and accept the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

For more information, please visit:
- Privacy Policy: https://autumntab.com/app-information/priv.html
- Terms of Use: https://autumntab.com/app-information/term.html
- About: https://autumntab.com/app-information/about.html
- Contact: https://autumntab.com/app-information/contacts.html
